data.description: REDUCTION:  30797 Dagsboro Road is located in a "country" setting, but only minutes away from shopping, entertainment, restaurants, etc.  This property offers 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms with living & dining rooms, kitchen, family room, laundry room, etc.  There's a large front porch and back sun deck not to mention 2 storage/shop buildings, etc. This home comes equipped with solar panels on the back roof to help with cost. The solar panels are leased through Solar City. Plenty of sunshine for gardens and room for outdoor toys and parking.  Time to take another look; this property is back on the market.  Call you agent now!
